# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Notebooks
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# OS
.DS_Store

# Env
.env
```

I removed `*.csv`, `*.joblib`, `*.safetensors`, and `*.json` because your app needs those files to run. Specifically, your Random Forest model (`.joblib`), DistilBERT weights (`.safetensors`), model configs (`.json`), and likely `spam.csv` are all required.

After editing, run:
```
git add .gitignore
git add Models/
git add spam.csv
git commit -m "Update gitignore and add model files"
git push origin main